        <section>
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3" style="font-family:'Cinzel',serif">1. Our Mission
            </h2>
            <p>Albion Maps was created to provide players with a simple and accessible way to explore information
                related
                to Albion Online. Our goal is to make game data easier to navigate, helping players quickly find useful
                information about maps, updates, and game changes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3" style="font-family:'Cinzel',serif">2. What We Do</h2>
            <p>We collect and organize publicly available information related to Albion Online, including patch notes,
                changelogs, and other relevant resources. The platform focuses on presenting this information in a clean
                and readable format so players can stay informed without unnecessary complexity.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3" style="font-family:'Cinzel',serif">3. Community Focus
            </h2>
            <p>Albion Maps exists for the community. The project was built by players who enjoy the game and wanted to
                create tools that make the experience better for others. We aim to keep the platform lightweight,
                accessible, and useful for both new and experienced players.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
